object.script:
frq1 = 0 frq2 = 0 frq3 = 0 frq4 = 0 frq5 = 0
function onTick()
tsx = input.getNumber(1) tsy = input.getNumber(2) tc = input.getBool(1) sgst1=input.getNumber(3)
up1 = tc and isPointInRectangle(tsx, tsy, 2,7,4,4) up2 = tc and isPointInRectangle(tsx, tsy, 7,7,4,4) up3 = tc and isPointInRectangle(tsx, tsy, 12,7,4,4) up4 = tc and isPointInRectangle(tsx, tsy, 22,7,4,4) up5 = tc and isPointInRectangle(tsx, tsy, 27,7,4,4)
dn1 = tc and isPointInRectangle(tsx, tsy, 2,16,4,4) dn2 = tc and isPointInRectangle(tsx, tsy, 7,16,4,4) dn3 = tc and isPointInRectangle(tsx, tsy, 12,16,4,4) dn4 = tc and isPointInRectangle(tsx, tsy, 22,16,4,4) dn5 = tc and isPointInRectangle(tsx, tsy, 27,16,4,4)
if up1 then frq1 = frq1+1 if frq1==10 then frq1 = 0 end end
if up2 then frq2 = frq2+1 if frq2==10 then frq2 = 0 end end
if up3 then frq3 = frq3+1 if frq3==10 then frq3 = 0 end end
if up4 then frq4 = frq4+1 if frq4==10 then frq4 = 0 end end
if up5 then frq5 = frq5+1 if frq5==10 then frq5 = 0 end end
if dn1 then frq1 = frq1-1 if frq1== -1 then frq1 = 9 end end
if dn2 then frq2 = frq2-1 if frq2== -1 then frq2 = 9 end end
if dn3 then frq3 = frq3-1 if frq3== -1 then frq3 = 9 end end
if dn4 then frq4 = frq4-1 if frq4== -1 then frq4 = 9 end end
if dn5 then frq5 = frq5-1 if frq5== -1 then frq5 = 9 end end
frq = (100*frq1)+(10*frq2)+(frq3)+(0.1*frq4)+(0.01*frq5)
output.setNumber(1,frq)
end
function onDraw() w = screen.getWidth() h = screen.getHeight()
screen.setColor(0, 2, 0) screen.drawRectF(0,0,32,32)
screen.setColor(0, 255, 0)
screen.drawText(2,1,"TACAN")
screen.drawText(2,11,frq1) screen.drawText(7,11,frq2) screen.drawText(12,11,frq3) screen.drawText(17,11,".") screen.drawText(22,11,frq4) screen.drawText(27,11,frq5)
screen.setColor(0,50,0) screen.drawRectF(3,22,(26*sgst1),7)
screen.setColor(0,255,0) screen.drawRect(3,22,26,7)
screen.setColor(0, 10, 0)
screen.drawRectF(3,8,2,2) screen.drawRectF(8,8,2,2) screen.drawRectF(13,8,2,2) screen.drawRectF(23,8,2,2) screen.drawRectF(28,8,2,2)
screen.drawRectF(3,17,2,2) screen.drawRectF(8,17,2,2) screen.drawRectF(13,17,2,2) screen.drawRectF(23,17,2,2) screen.drawRectF(28,17,2,2)
end
function isPointInRectangle(x, y, rectX, rectY, rectW, rectH) return x > rectX and y > rectY and x < rectX+rectW and y < rectY+rectH end

x1 = 0 y1 = 0 x2 = 0 y2 = 0 x3 = 0 y3 = 0
function onTick()
output.setBool(1,false) output.setBool(2,false) output.setBool(3,false)
tx = input.getNumber(1) ty = input.getNumber(2) keyx = input.getNumber(3) keyy = input.getNumber(4)
tc = input.getBool(1) w1 = input.getBool(2) w2 = input.getBool(3) w3 = input.getBool(4)
if w1==false and w2==false and w3==false then output.setBool(1,true) end
ipw1 = tc and isPointInRectangle(tx, ty, 11,0,6,7) ipw2 = tc and isPointInRectangle(tx, ty, 18,0,6,7) ipw3 = tc and isPointInRectangle(tx, ty, 25,0,6,7)
ipset= tc and isPointInRectangle(tx, ty, 0,24,15,5) iprst= tc and isPointInRectangle(tx, ty,16,24,16,5)
if ipw1 then output.setBool(1,true) end
if ipw2 then output.setBool(2,true) end
if ipw3 then output.setBool(3,true) end
if w1 and ipset then x1 = keyx y1 = keyy end
if w2 and ipset then x2 = keyx y2 = keyy end
if w3 and ipset then x3 = keyx y3 = keyy end
if w1 and iprst then x1 = 0 y1 = 0 end
if w2 and iprst then x2 = 0 y2 = 0 end
if w3 and iprst then x3 = 0 y3 = 0 end
if w1 then output.setNumber(1,x1) output.setNumber(2,y1) elseif w2 then output.setNumber(1,x2) output.setNumber(2,y2) elseif w3 then output.setNumber(1,x3) output.setNumber(2,y3) end
end
function isPointInRectangle(x, y, rectX, rectY, rectW, rectH) return x > rectX and y > rectY and x < rectX+rectW and y < rectY+rectH end
function onDraw() w = screen.getWidth() h = screen.getHeight()
screen.setColor(0, 2, 0) screen.drawRectF(0,0,32,32)
screen.setColor(0, 5, 0)
--1 screen.drawRectF(11,0,6,7) --2 screen.drawRectF(18,0,6,7) --3 screen.drawRectF(25,0,6,7)
if w1 then screen.setColor(0, 25, 0) screen.drawRectF(11,0,6,7) elseif w2 then screen.setColor(0, 25, 0) screen.drawRectF(18,0,6,7) elseif w3 then screen.setColor(0, 25, 0) screen.drawRectF(25,0,6,7) end
if ipset then screen.setColor(0, 25, 0) screen.drawRectF( 0,24,15,5) else screen.setColor(0, 5, 0) screen.drawRectF( 0,24,15,5) end
if iprst then screen.setColor(0, 25, 0) screen.drawRectF(16,24,16,5) else screen.setColor(0, 5, 0) screen.drawRectF(16,24,16,5) end
screen.setColor(0, 255, 0)
screen.drawText(1,1,"WP") screen.drawTextBox(12,1,4,5,"1",0,0) screen.drawTextBox(19,1,4,5,"2",0,0) screen.drawTextBox(26,1,4,5,"3",0,0)
screen.drawText(0,10,"X:") screen.drawText(0,16,"Y:")
if w1 then screen.drawText(9,10,math.floor(x1)) screen.drawText(9,16,math.floor(y1)) elseif w2 then screen.drawText(9,10,math.floor(x2)) screen.drawText(9,16,math.floor(y2)) elseif w3 then screen.drawText(9,10,math.floor(x3)) screen.drawText(9,16,math.floor(y3)) end
screen.drawTextBox( 0,24,16,5,"SET",0,0) screen.drawTextBox(16,24,16,5,"RES",0,0) end

sc = screen
nav = true tacan = false
function onTick()
ip = input.getBool(1) ix = input.getNumber(1) iy = input.getNumber(2)
inav = ip and isPointInRectangle(ix, iy, 3,1,26,9) itacan = ip and isPointInRectangle(ix, iy, 3,11,26,9)

if tacan == true then screen.setColor(0, 15, 0) sc.drawRectF(2,11,27,8) screen.setColor(0, 255, 0) sc.drawRect(2,11,27,8) sc.drawTextBox(3,11,26,9,"TACAN",0,0) else screen.setColor(0, 2, 0) sc.drawRectF(2,11,27,8) screen.setColor(0, 5, 0) sc.drawRect(2,11,27,8) sc.drawTextBox(3,11,26,9,"TACAN",0,0) end
screen.setColor(0, 255, 0) sc.drawText(1,22,"NAV") sc.drawText(15,22,"SEL") sc.drawText(29,22,".")
end

function onTick() P = input.getNumber(1) RL= input.getNumber(2) RU= input.getNumber(3) A = input.getNumber(4) S = input.getNumber(5) CL= input.getNumber(6) C = input.getNumber(7) al= input.getNumber(8) hd= input.getNumber(9) RL= RL*0.0174
LG = input.getBool(1) ali= input.getBool(2) hdi= input.getBool(3)
if GL then if (A < 150) and (CL < -1) then output.setBool(1, 1) end end
end
function onDraw() w = screen.getWidth() h = screen.getHeight()
